in that we are all different",

00:00:14.104 --> 00:00:14.904
they used to say.

00:00:14.905 --> 00:00:18.605
A pretty idiotic word game
that only increases confusion

00:00:18.606 --> 00:00:21.706
about the problem of human beings
in accepting what is different.

00:00:21.707 --> 00:00:25.607
Here is the testimony of
a singer that, from pop,

00:00:25.608 --> 00:00:28.108
suffers this problem in his career:

00:00:28.109 --> 00:00:30.509
the non-acceptance
of what is different.

00:00:31.010 --> 00:00:34.410
