tell you something… Look.

00:00:39.913 --> 00:00:41.813
Do you think
I'm not open enough?

00:00:41.814 --> 00:00:44.714
I don't accuse anyone. I just try
to make fun music. That is it.

00:00:44.815 --> 00:00:48.515
However, everyone is insisting
on the subject of discrimination.

00:00:49.016 --> 00:00:51.716
I repeat: I only want to see
the kids dance and have fun.

00:00:51.717 --> 00:00:53.817
